stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> drafting
    drafting --> script_ready : generate (LLM, validated JSON)
    script_ready --> script_ready : improve selection → keep (new version)
    script_ready --> script_ready : improve selection → revert (no change)
    script_ready --> script_ready : manual edit (new version)
    script_ready --> script_ready : restore older version
    script_ready --> drafting : scrap (confirm)
    script_ready --> accepted : accept (version frozen)
    accepted --> generating : generate video (mode chosen)
    generating --> done : job success
    generating --> accepted : job failed → retry
    done --> [*]
